### 1. Get List of All Releases
GET https://cactro-22-03-2026.vercel.app/api/releases

### 2. Create a New Release
POST https://cactro-22-03-2026.vercel.app/api/releases
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "v4.0.0-prod",
    "date": "15-06-2026 11:00",
    "additionalInfo": "Production release via REST Client"
}

### 3. Update (Edit) Steps and Notes
# Replace the 'id' parameter with a real ID from the GET request above
PATCH https://cactro-22-03-2026.vercel.app/api/releases?id=13
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "steps": ["merge", "changelog", "tests"],
    "notes": "Verified via external API call"
}

### 4. Delete a Release
# Replace the 'id' parameter with the ID you wish to remove
DELETE https://cactro-22-03-2026.vercel.app/api/releases?id=1